3. INSTALLATION

The library depends on ErrUt, which can be found here:
http://research.edm.uhasselt.be/jori/errut/errut.html

3.1 Unix-like platforms

Use the configure script and make to build the library. Run the configure
script with option '--help' to see which options can be specified.

3.2 Win32/WinCE

Project files for MS Visual Studio 8 are included in the library archive.
Take a look at the file 'nutconfig_win.h' to enable or disable some features.
You may have to tune the project settings to make sure the right locations
of other include files are set.

4. CONTACT

The library homepage can be found at the following location:
http://research.edm.uhasselt.be/enut/
		
You can reach the ENUt developers by sending an e-mail to
enutinfo@edm.uhasselt.be.

